OL,3,CDevon councillor expelled from Reform
OL,4,Cwas 'ostracised' by party, he says
OL,6,FA Devon councillor who has been
OL,7,Fexpelled by Reform UK claims he was
OL,8,F"systemically ostracised" by the Party
OL,9,Fafter reporting two fellow Reform
OL,10,Fcouncillors to the police over
OL,11,Felection expenses.
OL,13,FCllr Ed Hill, who represents Pinhoe
OL,14,Fand Mincinglake, has had his
OL,15,Fmembership revoked after writing to
OL,16,FMPs about free school meals and
OL,17,Fallegedly signing it from all Devon
OL,18,FReform councillors without their
OL,19,Fconsent.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
