OL,3,CDevon councillor expelled from Reform
OL,4,Cwas 'ostracised' by party, he says
OL,6,F"That Cllr Hill not only did this, but
OL,7,Fthen made the letter public -
OL,8,Fincluding sending it to the media and
OL,9,FMPs - meant disciplinary action was
OL,10,Finevitable."
OL,12,FIn May's local elections, Reform UK
OL,13,Fwon 18 seats on Devon County Council
OL,14,Fand became the second biggest party on
OL,15,Fthe authority behind the Liberal
OL,16,FDemocrats.
