OL,3,CDevon councillor expelled from Reform
OL,4,Cwas 'ostracised' by party, he says
OL,6,FThe first signs of division within the
OL,7,Fgroup came when Mr Hill reported two
OL,8,Fof his council colleagues - and an
OL,9,Felection agent - to the police over
OL,10,Felection expenses.
OL,12,FSince then, he claims he has been
OL,13,F"systemically ostracised from internal
OL,14,Fparty communication", including being
OL,15,Fremoved from WhatsApp groups, meetings
OL,16,Fand communication with colleagues.
