OL,3,CDevon councillor expelled from Reform
OL,4,Cwas 'ostracised' by party, he says
OL,6,FIn a WhatsApp exchange seen by ITV
OL,7,FWest Country, Mr Hill attempted to ask
OL,8,Fhis fellow Reform councillors if
OL,9,Fthey'd be happy to sign the letter
OL,10,Fabout free school meals, which was
OL,11,Faddressed to all of Devon's MPs and
OL,12,Fpublished on social media.
OL,14,FOne councillor said: "They will sign
OL,15,Fthe letter, they just won't join this
OL,16,Fgroup."
