OL,3,CDevon councillor expelled from Reform
OL,4,Cwas 'ostracised' by party, he says
OL,6,F"Since reporting a fellow Reform UK
OL,7,Fcouncillor to the police for suspected
OL,8,Felectoral offences, I have been
OL,9,Fsystematically ostracised from
OL,10,Finternal party communication ` removed
OL,11,Ffrom WhatsApp groups, excluded from
OL,12,Fmeetings, and shut out from
OL,13,Fcoordination with my own colleagues.
OL,14,FIf Reform UK had maintained proper
OL,15,Finternal channels, this situation
OL,16,Fwould never have occurred.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
