OL,4,Cwas 'ostracised' by party, he says
OL,6,FMr Hill will continue to represent
OL,7,FPinhoe and Mincinglake as an
OL,8,Findependent councillor and has
OL,9,Fappealed the decision to expel him
OL,10,Ffrom Reform UK.
OL,12,FRegarding the police report in
OL,13,Frelation to election expenses, Reform
OL,14,FUK says: "We understand an application
OL,15,Ffor relief is being submitted in
OL,16,Frespect of the election expense return
OL,17,Fof Cllr Neil Stevens and, on the basis
OL,18,Fof the information we have received,
OL,19,Fwe are confident this will be
OL,20,Fsuccessful."
